1.2.0
=====

Features:
- Added VPN configuration support (OpenVPN only for the moment).

Bugfixes:
- Commands are now case-insensitive.

Other:
- Created the changelog.
- Added install/update/uninstall instructions.

1.1.1
=====

Bugfixes:
- Configuration file location error.


1.1
===

Features:
- Supports custom IPv4 configuration, instead of DHCP.
- Supports custom DNS configuration.
- Makefile now supports updates to avoid overwritten configuration file.

Bugfixes:
- Minor corrections and typos in man pages.


1.0
===

Features:
- Scanning available wireless networks.
- Custom DHCP hostnames per network.
- Custom link layer address per network.
- Man pages.
